snippet: Ron Binz, President Obama’s nominee to be the nation’s top energy regulator, withdrew on Tuesday, conceding he did not have enough support for confirmation.
lead_paragraph: Ron Binz, President Obama’s nominee to be the nation’s top energy regulator, withdrew on Tuesday, conceding he did not have enough support for confirmation.
